# Ways to implement css
    - CSS (index.css)
    - SASS/SCSS (css with some superpowers)
    - Styled-Components(most of the big companies use this method. read documentation. It is package)
    - CSS frameworks/libraries - Ant Design, Material UI, Bootstrap, Chakra UI, Tailwind CSS etc..

# Tailwind CSS
    - npm install -D tailwindcss postcss
    - postcss is a tool to transform javascript into css. Tailwind use postcss behind the scenes.
    - It gives classnames for every css property you want to apply in your app.
